00:00.520 --> 00:05.990
And so, we Miburo became 
agents of the Aizu Domain.

00:06.130 --> 00:08.680
Whoa! The Shinsengumi were tough!

00:08.680 --> 00:10.770
You caught all the bad guys!

00:11.140 --> 00:12.850
Hey, Nagakura-sensei...

00:14.160 --> 00:15.670
Yes, Tsuru?

00:15.670 --> 00:19.120
Who was the strongest guy 
in the Shinsengumi?

00:19.320 --> 00:21.930
The strongest, huh?

00:24.150 --> 00:25.870
That reminds me...

00:28.790 --> 00:31.390
Who among us is truly strong?

00:32.000 --> 00:34.410
When the dust settles, 
who will be left standing?

00:35.110 --> 00:39.080
We'll find out with the first ever 
Grand Miburo Drinking Contest!

